description:
Ever wonder how @MrBeast coordinates a lambo airlift or bear logistics? In this video, go *Inside the Beast* where we break down the Slackbot integrations and team management frameworks that allow the world's biggest YouTuber to find experts and manage million-dollar productions. 

As a personal agent inside @Slackhq Slackbot can summarize conversations and preserve the reasoning behind them. Teams use it to retrace past decisions, pull context, and turn scattered discussions into clear next steps.

Learn more about how MrBeast uses Slackbot to turn his ideas into actions: https://slack.com/lp/mrbeast 
 Watch more episodes from Inside the Beast: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLnobS_RgN7JZAhVg871pjR1varMRLMprh
